name: Verify Biljettvaljaren E2E Case 1
fullName: Test Suites.Page Biljettvaljaren.Verify Biljettvaljaren E2E Case 1
description:
Test steps:
1. Traveler category: Adult
2. Route: Jönköping Juneporten - Huskvarna Esplanaden
3. Travel habits: 2/day, 5/week, 4/month, 12/year
4. Calculate price
5. Verify that 2 suggestions appear
6. Verify that the correct suggestions appear
7. Verify the links work
